{"tid":1523150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府回應暴力示威活動 190831","createTime":"2019-08-31T15:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T00:55:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":134,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"2243594cd0b7772ba13b4300cf6296098964444b","tid":1523150,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:26:31.000Z","msg":"政府回應暴力示威活動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  政府發言人就今日（八月三十一日）在港島和九龍多區的示威活動作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n  今日有大量人士在警方發出反對通知書的情況下，在港島和九龍多區進行未經批准的集結和遊行示威，廣泛堵塞主要道路，導致港島區交通接近癱瘓，嚴重影響緊急服務及市民日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n  激進示威者在多區與警方對峙，向添馬政府總部、立法會大樓和警察總部以及在不同地方投擲多枚汽油彈，並以腐蝕性液體及磚頭等襲擊警務人員。激進示威者在多處縱火、破壞公物、架起路障、破壞月台幕門等港鐵站設施；軒尼詩道的火勢一度十分猛烈，非常危險。激進示威者這些暴力行為嚴重擾亂社會安寧，對在場執法的警務人員和市民的人身安全構成極大的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n  激進示威者的違法及暴力行為持續升級，罔顧市民大眾的安全，特區政府予以嚴厲譴責，警方亦必定嚴正追究。特區政府將繼續維護法治，並且再次呼籲廣大市民一同向暴力說「不」，讓社會盡快回復秩序。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月31日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間23時13分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/31/P2019083100919.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F31%2FP2019083100919.htm&d=30ZlKbyCH33W3wkrfz60C4Vo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=468f2cf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/31/P2019083100919.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2e60334a0a1efac1b66ed93994c6af8561a123d8","tid":1523150,"uid":128271,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />copy稿 改下日期又出<br />\n政府新聞處咁撚易做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa55e221b04b984263007db7435f71b15c24b41","tid":1523150,"uid":4206,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"說好了的緊急令呢？"},{"pid":"9e4613562d6496f0a7bd243e3f649842a1bb147f","tid":1523150,"uid":15880,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:28:54.000Z","msg":"wfc 香港冇無政府左三個月"},{"pid":"d3ae55cb8a27122960f4a333bc7f162c1dc6f35a","tid":1523150,"uid":98673,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"緊急法呢"},{"pid":"c3d55b9100ee19fe3a8f8fc58f8643eb0b45741d","tid":1523150,"uid":136467,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"2acc95bc934c9a4cb7bdbf8bdf5090da9e8890c2","tid":1523150,"uid":202137,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:30:10.000Z","msg":"向警暴說不?"},{"pid":"948d41c81d41ac6b06b8722bd4735f4636c3f117","tid":1523150,"uid":136467,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:30:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">在場執法的警務人員對市民的人身安全構成極大的威脅。</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f722687ebe6e593372f13b2a76a7222eebde060","tid":1523150,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"不"},{"pid":"01234efe1211254d3b08479253afa635d2886171","tid":1523150,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:32:17.000Z","msg":"垃圾文"},{"pid":"93348cc45c074839999b5926629dfdbf3acb9f53","tid":1523150,"uid":114801,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0f722687ebe6e593372f13b2a76a7222eebde060","tid":1523150,"uid":114801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"不"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:32:20.000Z","msg":"我說左「不」喇<br />\n<br />\n林鄭可以回應五大訴求未"},{"pid":"57999c69b621e7a79ad65813bbfd4826abc7630c","tid":1523150,"uid":273466,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hXRBMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hXRBMD.jpg&h=062eb1d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/065GYZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F065GYZY.jpg&h=c2190161&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HcbyP6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail